                                        d="M12.9925 0.539943C10.1473 0.539943 7.79619 1.34037 6.15448 2.98209C4.51277 4.62381 3.71048 6.97866 3.71048 9.82381C3.71048 12.6689 4.51277 15.0238 6.15448 16.6655C7.79619 18.3073 10.1473 19.1095 12.9925 19.1095C15.8358 19.1095 18.1888 18.3073 19.8305 16.6655C21.4722 15.0238 22.2726 12.6689 22.2726 9.82381C22.2726 6.97866 21.4703 4.62381 19.8305 2.98394C18.1888 1.34223 15.8376 0.538086 12.9925 0.538086M11.9636 6.18937C12.3722 5.08437 13.884 5.05094 14.274 6.16151C14.4225 6.59051 14.5525 7.05294 14.6843 7.60637C15.2693 7.60081 15.7652 7.60637 16.235 7.63237C17.4162 7.69737 17.888 9.13109 16.9333 9.82937C16.7105 9.99104 16.4832 10.1465 16.2518 10.2955C16.1097 10.3877 16.0016 10.5237 15.9436 10.6828C15.8855 10.842 15.881 11.0157 15.9305 11.1776C16.0735 11.6364 16.1886 12.0505 16.2833 12.4554C16.5526 13.5883 15.34 14.4666 14.4002 13.7739C13.9402 13.4305 13.5034 13.0571 13.0928 12.6559C12.6849 13.0376 12.2558 13.396 11.8076 13.7294C10.8605 14.4239 9.61991 13.5548 9.89477 12.4126C9.98762 12.0264 10.1028 11.6289 10.2458 11.1869C10.2984 11.0231 10.2954 10.8467 10.2373 10.6847C10.1792 10.5228 10.0692 10.3847 9.92449 10.2918C9.67564 10.132 9.43162 9.96476 9.19277 9.79037C8.25119 9.09766 8.70991 7.68066 9.87805 7.62123C10.3665 7.59523 10.881 7.59337 11.5012 7.60637C11.659 7.06781 11.8058 6.6128 11.9636 6.18937ZM0.0667659 20.4894C0.716766 18.8588 1.76977 17.3786 2.88219 16.1418C3.31862 16.9255 3.86091 17.6516 4.51277 18.3054C5.8239 19.6165 7.42848 20.4783 9.20577 20.9555C8.27966 22.4576 7.60588 24.1012 7.21119 25.8213C7.16881 26.0026 7.07287 26.167 6.93584 26.2932C6.79881 26.4193 6.62702 26.5013 6.44279 26.5285C6.25856 26.5557 6.0704 26.5269 5.90273 26.4458C5.73507 26.3648 5.59567 26.2351 5.50262 26.0738L3.45234 22.5266L0.672195 21.7244C0.547511 21.6884 0.431733 21.6268 0.332325 21.5435C0.232917 21.4601 0.152086 21.3568 0.0950435 21.2403C0.038001 21.1237 0.0060133 20.9965 0.0011428 20.8668C-0.00372769 20.7373 0.0186271 20.6099 0.0667659